parameter.name: Display Text
parameter.val: It is possible to complete Therium-2 without getting heard or entering combat; you just have to find out how.

parameter.name: Display Text
parameter.val: Throwing enemies off the sides of the crete in Therium-2 will result in those enemies guaranteed death; but it will also guarantee that your no kills challenge will return as false.

parameter.name: Display Text
parameter.val: You do not need to approach enemies; be it stealth or combat. You only need to get to the end of each level (or open world branch).
